notes on this project

canonical_cards table:
10 - reverse
11 - skip
12 - +2
13 - wild
14 - +4

games table:
play_direction:
true = ascending
false = descending

game_deck:
user_id:
if positive int, then it is a user id, it is
in that players hand

        if 0 in draw deck
        if -1 card has been played
        if -2 then top is on top of the played deck,
        play on this card
